item.description: Robotic Pirate Monkey is well-known for their fresh, innovative sound and high-energy live performances. The trio has played numerous festivals and sold out shows throughout the country. Teaming with the rising VOODOO FARM out of New York City and one of Boston's best DJ's in Richard Fraioli, the event is set up to be an unforgettable night with an act unlike Boston has ever seen. Here's a link to more information and videos: http://www.seektheroy...
item.name: Robotic Pirate Monkey w/ VOODOO FARM + Richard Fraioli
